      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>Legacy Odyssey is a subscription-based platform that enables users to create digital baby books and family photo albums hosted on custom domains or subdomains. The Service includes a mobile application, web-based book viewer, photo storage, and domain management.</p>

      <h2>3. Account Registration</h2>
